metadata.name: Aurora Kiss
metadata.description:
Aurora falls in love with a man from the earth, but she knew she could never reach him, until one day she gathers all her energy and feelings to express her love for him.
She Danced for him even when he was at sleep, sanding above his bed and looked at his beautiful face, she Smiled and Giggled. 

She felt TRUST, HOPE and LOVE within her...
She knew there would be a great journey ahead of them that they can enjoy every moment of the it together, 
She Knew she would appreciate every single moment of it,

So she closed her eyes and tenderly kissed his lips...

( Original and Physical oil painting )
